column5: A lot are from this guys who's travelling coast to coast taking pics of huts for a coffee table book.  http://www.icehuts.ca/mobile#_portfolios_a1  Lots from simcoe, and a lot of cool ones. I know I'm keeping my eye open for the book when it's published.
Awesome shacks!  Very well done.  I like the one with the dormers.
I like the ones that will fit right into the back of a pick up!
x2 Have a good week All  Paul
Nice variety,some are in move in condition
